How to implement multiple notes in a line:
Step 1: Edit the melodybeat code and delete the note replacing code. Then, change the new note code to create a period between notes rather than placing an f.
Step 2:Edit the prebeatread code to move to the next note when it detects a period.
Step 3: Test to see if it can send two melody beats at relatively the same time. And then 3.
Step 4: Create a conversion script that converts the old code to the new code.
